Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boys, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans aren’t such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who needs tomorrow anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don’t hide your fists
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not old enough
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to sell your dreams away to uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boys, you’re the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who can pull the trigger in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re living in this senseless, ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,awesome world right at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t forget every truth or lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re way too young to die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this empty town lined with empty faces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids took off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into this windless night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they want to change something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with…this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the best you’ve got…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is all you’ve got,\NI still don’t need to use that…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven’t realized it?\NI…haven’t used my Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have enough strength\Nor desire…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you are weak?\NBecause you don’t have enough…hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I kept playing comrade with you guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn’t have…been able to get…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…this much power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right…I need …
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both power…and hatred…\Nin order to catch up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:04:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers:\N                     Distance Among the Uchiha
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother…I’ll get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t push it…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place…\Nwhere Father works, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…The headquarters\Nof the Leaf Police Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was curious about it from before,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but why’s the Uchiha Clan crest\Non the Police Force mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… so you noticed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…Let me see…\NTo put it simply…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems the previous generations\Nof the Uchiha Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,set up and established the Police Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they used their own crest for\Nthe symbol mark of this organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From olden times,\Nthe Uchiha Clan has always been
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in charge of protecting\Nthe public and the peace of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:05:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Uchiha crest is\Na testament to the proud clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Uchiha Clan has gotten small now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even now, nearly all members\Nbelong to this first force here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and contribute to maintaining\Npeace in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only even more exceptional Shinobi\Ncan crack down on the crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,committed by Shinobi, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure enough, father’s awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaf Police Force\N		Are you going to enter\N		the Police Force, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…I’m not sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I grow up, I’m also going\Nto enter the Police Force, so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father’s also coming to\Ntomorrow’s entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the first step to my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re late…What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to talk to you about.\NCome quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve come this far just half a year\Nafter being promoted to Chunin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About tomorrow’s special mission…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve decided to go with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you complete this mission, Itachi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your entrance into\Nthe Anbu Black Ops is almost assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to be so worried.\NMore importantly…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow’s my…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow’s mission will be\Na very important mission not just for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the Uchiha Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m quitting tomorrow’s mission, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing talking insanity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know how important\Na day tomorrow is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to Sasuke’s Academy\Nentrance ceremony tomorrow…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The general rule is for relatives\Nto attend the Academy entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was the notice, right… Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go to the Academy…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your left leg…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to ice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother… He’s so distant…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Congratulations\Non your entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, please work very hard\Ntowards striving for the Shinobi path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I’d like you to bring further prosperity\Nto the Hidden Village in the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee… I remember\Nthe time when Itachi entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I’d expect from his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help with both boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first prodigy since the beginning\Nof the Academy…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were no students\Nas exceptional as that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a bit too much praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m hopeful for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become a fine Shinobi\Nlike your big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…That’s Uchiha, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder…if he’s awesome, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm…Must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recess at last! What a drag.\NI’m still not used to this place…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want some too, Shikamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, all of your recesses\Nhave become meal times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s my boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve great confidence\Nyou’ll make it great in Anbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This won’t do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won’t do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got a long way…to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest your body\Non your days off at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to push it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard…that Big Brother graduated\Nfrom the Academy in just one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The times are different, then and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, that kid is a bit special, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s my boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I’m going to hand out\Nthe report cards for the first half.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taijutsu: 1st in class and academy\NNinjutsu: 1st in class and academy\N		lndividual rank: 1st in class and academy\N		Team rank: 1st in class and academy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do a fine job in this vein like\Nyour big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father… I wanted you to say,\N“That’s my boy,” to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you can’t participate\Nin the assembly tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t understand your own position!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m setting out on a mission tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re they doing this late\Nat night with the lights off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t say…\Nlt’s a top secret mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itachi…You also have the role\Nof the pipe which connects the clan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the keystone of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that well in mind!\NAnd come to tomorrow’s assembly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to bed after\Nyou’ve gone to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing hanging around\Nthis late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Report Card
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father only thinks about you, Big Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I loathsome to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s logical for Shinobi to be\Nill-thought of by people, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how I feel…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:13:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother's right.\NI really do…think ill of him…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellence is not easy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have power,\Nyou become alienated and also arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you’re coveted\Nand sought after at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, we only have each other\Nfor siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will continue to exist with you\Nas a wall you must get over…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I’m ill-thought of…\NThat’s what a big brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Itachi home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to\Ntalk to you about. Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why’s everyone gathered here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two people who didn’t come\Nto yesterday’s assembly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t you come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn’t go to the assembly Father\Nwas talking about last night, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that when you enter Anbu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you get roped into various\Ntroublesome things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father also said something\Nlike that in your defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for us, we don’t intend\Nto treat you special.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I shall be careful next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I’m going to have\Nto ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right… But before that,\Nthere’s a little more I want to ask you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s about Shisui Uchiha who threw himself\Ninto the Nakano River to kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Threw himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other person who didn’t come\Nto the assembly is that Shisui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, you adored him\Nlike a real older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see… I hadn’t seen him at all recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we the Police Force have decided\Nto launch an all-out investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the will Shisui wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The analysis of the handwriting\Nhas been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No mistake, he did indeed write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are no murder leads,\Nthen what’s the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’d be easy for a person who can use\NSharingan to copy handwriting, you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most adept Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man feared as Shisui,\N“the Instantaneous Man.”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a man who would take\Nthe lead no matter what the mission
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if it was for the sake of the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s tough to think that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,such a man would leave something\Nlike this and kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn’t judge people…\Nonly on looks and speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being,\NI leave the will with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that and you request cooperation\Nin the investigation from Anbu Black Ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we get a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we have a different route\Nto Anbu Black Ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll know right away if you do something\Nlike crushing the investigation request.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don’t you just come right out\Nand say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You suspect me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That’s right, you little punk…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try doing something\Nlike betraying the clan and…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it’ll cost you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn’t judge people…\Nonly on looks and speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s because you take the liberty to\Njudge me as patient and take me lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clan…Clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You measure incorrectly\Nthe size of your own vessels
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:17:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and don’t know the depth of mine,\Nso you grovel there…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never seen him like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shisui…was monitoring you recently…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half a year after entering Anbu…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the strangeness of your behavior\Ncouldn’t be overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fixated on the organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fixated on the clan,\Nfixated on the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a dreadful thing that constrains oneself\Nand labels one’s own vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it’s a foolish thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that fear and hate…\Nwhat one has never seen or known…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell’s the matter\Nwith you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itachi…\NYou’ve been a little strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not strange at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m carrying out my own role…\NThat’s it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn’t you come last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to elevate myself higher…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you talking about…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My vessel is dismayed\Nat this foolish clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From olden times,\Nthe Uchiha Clan has all along
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,been in charge protecting\Nthe peace of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Uchiha crest is a testament\Nto the proud clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s my boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve great confidence\Nyou’ll do great in Anbu Black Ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're fixated\Non insignificant things like clans…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you lose sight of what’s truly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True change cannot be made if stuck\Nwithin the restrictions of regulations,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and constrained predictions\Nand imagination…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying such arrogant things!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! You’ll be imprisoned\Nif you say any more foolish nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellence is not easy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have power,\Nyou become alienated and also arrogant…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you’re coveted\Nand sought after at first…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why… Big Brother…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t tolerate it anymore…\NCaptain, order imprisonment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother! Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not the one who killed Shisui.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I apologize for\Nmy numerous slips of the tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m very sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, it seems he’s been up\Nto his ears in Anbu Black Ops missions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was a little tired…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Anbu Black Ops is a force\Nunder the direct control of Lord Hokage…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even we the Police Force can’t arrest him,\Nif we don’t have an arrest warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as for Itachi…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take the responsibility\Nand monitor him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you’ve woken up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a hindrance back at that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it won’t be like that this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll show you…\Nthe true power of Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I recalled the parts one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt as though\NI had understood everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faded words which I kept so close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this distant yearning for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live, simply repeating this cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Held in my two hands\NA droplet of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Softly clutching forgotten memories\NLost words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll keep these thoughts…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me all you've got,\NNaruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is this all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.49,0:23:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were talking impudently\Nabout your Way of Ninja
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding! Right now,\Nyou're not even worth beating!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode:\N“Father and Son, the Broken Crest”
